2.  (1)  A person shall be deemed to be connected if—
(a)  they are officers or directors of one another’s business;
(b)  they are legally recognized partners in business;
(c)  any one person directly or indirectly owns, controls, or holds five per cent
or more of the outstanding voting stock or shares of both of them;
(d)  one of them directly or indirectly controls the other;
(e)  both of them are directly or indirectly controlled by a third person;
(f)
together they directly or indirectly control a third person; or
